# Test-only sshd config. Deliberately permissive so the integration matrix can
# exercise password auth, TCP forwarding, and SFTP. Do not use anywhere real.
Port 2222
AddressFamily inet
PermitRootLogin no
PasswordAuthentication yes
PubkeyAuthentication yes
KbdInteractiveAuthentication no
UsePAM no
AllowTcpForwarding yes
GatewayPorts clientspecified
PermitTunnel yes
Subsystem sftp internal-sftp
LogLevel VERBOSE
